name: Komowata Haruka(こもわた遙華) CG Style Checkpoint
description:
This is a checkpoint model of art style of Komowata Haruka(こもわた遥華), an illustrator who is focused on SD illustration (chibi).

Dataset is from Yuzusoft galgames, including Senren Banka, Riddle Joker, and Cafe Stella.

Informations:

  1. Training set is made of SD CGs, which means chibi promote is suitable for better experience;

  2. There is relatively lack of front view images in dataset, so this model tend to create side-viewed images and overfitted images when promotions are made up with only characteristics. It would be better to describe the scene or camera when inputing promotes;

  3. Although this is a model made with chibi, it can still create normal ratio characters with visible komowata-haruka-style. If that's what you needed, try to put chibi in negative promotes.

  4. This model is avaliable for generating nsfw images, but actually the dataset does not contain nsfw images, so I can't pledge the effect and level of fit at the same time.

  5. This model is made at Dec. 19th, 2022.
